{"tid":1427700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【戰術討論】應該點打警犬先啱","createTime":"2019-08-07T07:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T07:36:52.000Z","uid":301460,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ae8d212ebb944a2c96732aa6867bd79582fe899c","tid":1427700,"uid":301460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:24:48.000Z","msg":"每次警署衝擊都有好多勇武手足比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋都有自己家庭，學業<br />\n一旦比人拉一次，好可能以後都唔敢出黎<br />\n希望各位手足去之前睇下呢個po，分好工再去<br />\n記住我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一個都不能少！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我先</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">消防隊二至三人一組</span><br />\n通常警犬都係放催淚彈，再向前衝<br />\n好多手足撲彈既時候比人拉<br />\n如果大家可以分翻組，有人撲火，有人睇情形<br />\n當警犬黎既時候拉佢走或者爭取時間比人走<br />\n係咪可以減少手足比人拉既機會？<br />\n<br />\n利申：第一次開po，大家有怪莫怪"},{"pid":"f842699b03f498b8e0ad9b99aca1e84a3e557439","tid":1427700,"uid":268019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:25:18.000Z","msg":"唔係講好左錫春袋咩?"},{"pid":"2ffdf51110c1f1ab5f339faba0d8abb87279ff92","tid":1427700,"uid":301460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f842699b03f498b8e0ad9b99aca1e84a3e557439","tid":1427700,"uid":268019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:25:18.000Z","msg":"唔係講好左錫春袋咩?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:27:40.000Z","msg":"我奶開"},{"pid":"c35c6f225a3407591dfc151cdebc53c8c66b31f1","tid":1427700,"uid":301460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:29:01.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"ba5ef3b0a257a9fcb31baf503b97aa186f1ec8a0","tid":1427700,"uid":301460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:32:21.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"8e273f4ebb043d3cff9bf793289a87046463c709","tid":1427700,"uid":301460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:32:32.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"99ac80ef045f75fd6b547da2870a3099b307bdc3","tid":1427700,"uid":